-Site surveys: sample existing wireless spectrum, layout a plan of how strong is the wireless signal depending of placement also called heat map.
-Mobile Device Management (MDM): manage company-owned and user-owned mobile devices.
-Bring your owwn device (BYOD): when an employee bring his own device for work. The device need to meet the company's requirements.
-Corporate Owned Personlly Enabled (COPE): it's a device bough by the company, but the employee use it both for work and as a personal device. The organization keeps full
control of the device.
-Choose Your Own Device (CYOD): similar to COPE, but the user choses the device.
